Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  我只覺得這個像炸魚排
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太這個大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來冬海同學的可愛萬人迷程度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是完全敵不過銳太的遲鈍程度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來那你的可愛萬人迷程度又怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是動物園裡的無尾熊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰是「小熊餅」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}註：指「樂天小熊餅」的無尾熊圖案設計
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪有說  難道你還是巧克力夾心的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做這種戀愛頭腦才會做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你意圖何在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了向別人顯示我們的「男女朋友」關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  那三個人完全沒有看過來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都玩得正歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,52)\fn@方正准圆_GBK\frz-90\fs16\3c9D86D0}彈珠汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過味道本身只是一般般
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調味醬也只有鹹味而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全說不上美味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麵糊了這一點最致命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不可思議的是讓人吃起來欲罷不能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  難得說了中二以外的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海邊吃什麼都美味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道偏重難道是考慮到了那些剛游完泳很累的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銳太同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你準備一下甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  銳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要劈得像可愛萬人迷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銳太要使出可愛萬人迷流劍術  完全不在話下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為可愛萬人迷風紀委員  就讓我來給你劈西瓜打個分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼可愛萬人迷  可愛萬人迷的  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  棍子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請動用腦袋來劈西瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是讓我用智慧來解決嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是讓你用額頭狠命砸下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是物理性的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊  來啊  銳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊  在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銳太  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是冥界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,季堂同學  是這邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽從風紀委員的話一定沒錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  銳太同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:06:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在混淆視聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確的只有我這個女朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有夏川的話不能相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長是暗黑邪神  混沌魔王  惡魔將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心啊  這個女人可是會讓季堂同學墮落的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信我的「女友」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(180,350)\fs22}不要過去  銳太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,350)\fs22}說什麼傻話  等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}不行啊  銳  真的不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真涼  西瓜在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝這邊直走3公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請飛撲過來拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,350)\fs22}給我等一下啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}銳  不是那邊  是這裡啊  銳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(180,350)\fs22}…那邊是怒之黑暗  回來  快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜到手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上最柔軟的  純白的西瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  銳太同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都不來抱緊我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,130)\fn@方正粗圆_GBK\frz-90\fs18\1c807977\bord0}不要臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  被鐫刻的罪之烙印嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有麵糊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  請銳太同學更換一下吊燈的燈泡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈絲好像斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  夏川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和季堂同學交往之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就沒再被別人表白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有看到過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在體育館後面被表白後嘆氣的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男生真是氣勢洶洶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很討厭那種被拒之後就反過來發怒的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老碰上那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確會讓人開始討厭被表白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想乾脆隨便找個人交往也完全可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  如果是以此為目的才和季堂同學交往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能無法原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相到底是怎樣的  夏川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬海同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋蔥要剝到什麼程度才算好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要剝到最裡面去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要剝掉褐色的那層皮就夠了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  難怪剝起來沒個底了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在變成這樣之前不問問我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再碰蔬菜了  給我去洗米吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  別用洗潔精啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會在洗米的時候用洗潔精啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你老把事情搞砸我才這麼說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說出那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不做蠢事  我也不會那樣想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要決定性的證據呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  聽不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要給她們看看決定性的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在交往的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那種東西  就算你突然這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:10:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送禮物之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用實物可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更有衝擊性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要那種她們一看就會相信的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝擊性…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈風斬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用烈風斬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.99,0:11:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈風斬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說接吻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在眾目睽睽之下裝作若無其事的樣子比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是日常功課一般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.96,0:11:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是很自然地打個招呼一般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你來吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  為什麼這麼吃驚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已經吻過好多次了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區接吻  對我們這種反對戀愛的人來說並沒有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對她們這些戀愛頭腦來說可是很有衝擊性的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這會讓事態發展成什麼樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  會變成修羅場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說得這麼事不關己  這可是三人份啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  正如你所說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說這次我就給你一個「選擇權」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會拿筆記本的秘密當盾牌來強迫你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是選擇接吻還是選擇不接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你來決定  季堂銳太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銳你好弱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅心三是這張哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你不擅長記東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是  啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃如下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和大家度過愉快的時間以後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先說著「我累了  先去休息」站起身來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨後我會說「晚安  親愛的」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在我耳邊輕聲說一句「啊  晚安  甜心」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後順勢吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當是歐美情侶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銳？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  沒有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家呢  還行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我倒是沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}啊  沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果吻了真涼  就是直奔修羅場路線了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}話說剛才的郵件是發給米歇爾的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果不吻她而選擇趨近後宮路線
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}是噢  如果不每天發郵件的話  他會寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}米歇爾怕寂寞？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}是噢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌關係暴露也就只是時間問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我覺得有點累  先去休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  說出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼啊  你不用配合我結束啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦  反正也玩膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  今天我有東西想交給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給銳  這個給夏川
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五個人都一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姬兒負責設計的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便說一句  那可不是字母「Z」而是「乙女」的「乙」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}註：日語中少女寫作「乙女」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大師找到了能給我們製作的店家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提議的是千和哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想  體育社團大都會有統一的制服之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是咱們社團沒有那種東西呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好不容易成為正式社團了  這樣實在有點寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就和她們倆商量了看看可以做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事對夏川同學保密了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟你是建立這個社團的功臣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就當是社員送給你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連我都保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是告訴銳  不就洩露給夏川了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撒謊能力超級差的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是選美大賽了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決出勝負之後再送也不太方便
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想趁現在送啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來千和她們之所以互相聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了攪和我們的關係  而是為了這件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗給你們了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們送我這個飽含心意的吊飾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那種情況下我沒辦法吻你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候你要是強吻的話  我一定會鄙視你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不由得感動了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也重新認識到自己是多麼醜陋的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這只是碰巧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春咲同學她們在敵視我的同時  還能夠送禮物給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠為敵視的對手送上這樣的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們就是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我實在是差太遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的選美大賽  拿不了第一了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆棄權吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我也想過  但考慮到她們的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是應該如期現身參賽  然後接受審判吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被我搶走以後  春咲同學有多麼懊悔  多麼傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮到這點  我就無法不戰而敗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\an7\pos(70,10)\fn@方正准圆_GBK\frz-90\fs20\1c926F74\bord0}九月十日  晴\N我要成為醫生\N治好千和的身體!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你陪我到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次合宿結束以後  你就自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長還是沒起床
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明昨天還很有精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還能參加選美嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾點開始來著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16點進場  16點半開演呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參賽者要在15點半之前在特設舞台前集合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前  她應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們先去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒一定要來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真涼  你還在睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餓了吧  要不要吃點掛麵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  現在能讓我一個人待會兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒辣的太陽  in the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心也  in the blu…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}躲開  躲開  躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.81,0:18:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我啊  癡漢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噁心宅男  噁心處男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  處男嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說這是最棒的誇獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噁心  噁心  噁心  噁心  噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死  去死  去死  去死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處男去死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  再來幾句
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  難得的勝地度假全毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有錢人就該去國外啊  國外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種地方早就去過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且這裡也不是你這種人該待的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煩人  我是來合宿的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小涼也來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小涼怎麼樣了啊  身體好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是在意  其實我只是有義務向爸爸匯報而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說你還是很喜歡真涼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴  處男
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  發生了這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小涼她一直被稱作「夏川家的寶石」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶石  也就是「裝飾品」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸在交際界用來炫耀的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小涼和她母親拆散  帶到自己身邊也正是為了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小涼的舉手投足正如父親期待的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美地演繹了一個聰明端莊  又尊敬父親的溫順女兒形象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣的  爸爸完全不抱期待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小涼她卻能做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  她就努力扮演爸爸所期待的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後變成了怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小涼不斷欺騙著自己  結果漸漸失去了真實的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小涼說的話都相當荒謬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才剛說完非常苛刻的話  下一秒又變溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後又變得冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也被折騰得夠嗆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都被她折騰著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這也並不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的日子並不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你能喜歡上我的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  如果有能和真涼在一起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得那會是什麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.00,0:21:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和騙子在一起的  那還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:21:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫兇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嬌小姐選美大賽現在開始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.76,0:23:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集的可愛萬人迷道具是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率真的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.27,0:23:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有再多的話語交流
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果內容空洞無物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.92,0:23:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎麼率真
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.65,0:23:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是毫無意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.07,0:23:39.91,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fnArial}# 13{\r}  走向新世界的修羅場
